@startuml
title User Flow — Complete Study Session
start

:Launch NextLearn;
:Load settings from YAML;
:Create guest user (first run);
:Scan decks directory recursively;
:Sync deck metadata to DB;
:Display home screen with deck list;

:User views deck cards\n(search/filter using prefixes);

:User selects a deck;

:Load deck from file;
:Load user progress from DB;
:Build HTML from page content;
:Enrich with KaTeX & highlight.js;
:Load HTML into WebView;
:Show learning view;

repeat
  :User reads page content;
  :User navigates pages\n(N/P, arrows, ← →);
  :User scrolls content\n(J/K, C-v/M-v);
  :Progress saved to DB\nafter each navigation;
  :User interacts with features\n(Falcon Eye, zoom, images, links\ncommand palette, handbook);
repeat while (more pages?) is (yes)

:User presses Q/D/Esc to exit;

:Save final progress to DB;
:Record daily activity\n(pages viewed, minutes);
:Return to home screen;

:User closes app;
:Log.CloseAndFlush() writes logs;
stop
@enduml
